                <img width="800" height="383" src="https://neerajbhagat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/investment-800x383.jpg" class="attachment-simpleasy-featured-image size-simpleasy-featured-image wp-post-image" alt="Setting up subsidiary outside India" srcset="https://neerajbhagat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/investment-800x383.jpg 800w, https://neerajbhagat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/investment-480x230.jpg 480w, https://neerajbhagat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/investment-768x368.jpg 768w, https://neerajbhagat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/investment.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" />            </a>
